-tests with 5 expected SQLite-only skips, frontend ran 173 tests, and PostgreSQL acceptance ran the
-fixed five-test suite twice with zero skips. No production code, migration, or API contract changed
-in repair.
+Evidence is under `.ralph/runs/2026-07-12_133148_normal_run/`. Focused red/green logs cover the
+public registry read seam, duplicates, action parity, and complete form variants. No migration or
+new dependency was required.
 
